<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.6.4">
<l>aṇaṅkeṉa vāṭume ṉaṅkam</l>
<l>vaṇaṅki vaḻipaṭu mīcaṉ</l>
<l>piṇaṅki yamarar pitaṟṟuṅ</l>
<l>kuṇaṅkeḻu koḷkaiyi ṉāṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Like a demon dances my body;</l>
<l>it bows [and] worships the lord,</l>
<l>according to the meritorious tenet</l>
<l>by which the immortals rave in unison.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
